IX messages\n   - Handles FIX message extraction from Exchange body/headers\n\n7. **`/workspace/components/camel-fix/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/fix/FixConsumer.java`**\n   - Consumer class extending DefaultConsumer\n   - Receives inbound FIX messages\n   - Implements onFixMessage() callback for processing messages\n   - Properly manages lifecycle with doStart/doStop methods\n\n### Modified Files\n\n1. **`/workspace/components/pom.xml`**\n   - Added `<module>camel-fix</module>` in alphabetical order (line 139)\n   - Positioned between `camel-file-watch` and `camel-flatpack`",
